msgstr "FieldTM | Field Tasking Manager"

#: app/templates/landing.html:491
msgid "Coordinate field campaigns"
msgstr "Ratibu kampeni za uwanjani"

#: app/templates/landing.html:492
msgid "FIELD - TASKING MANAGER"
msgstr "FIELD - TASKING MANAGER"

#: app/templates/landing.html:494
msgid ""
"Enhancing field mapping efficiency and accuracy through seamless "
"coordination."
msgstr ""
"Kuongeza ufanisi na usahihi wa uchoraji ramani wa uwanjani kupitia uratibu "
"usio na vikwazo."

#: app/templates/landing.html:497
msgid "Explore Projects"
msgstr "Chunguza miradi"

#: app/templates/landing.html:509
msgid "Loading metrics..."
msgstr "Vipimo vinapakiwa..."

#: app/templates/landing.html:517
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr "Ni nini hiki?"

#: app/templates/landing.html:519
msgid ""
"The Field Tasking Manager (Field-TM) helps teams add local knowledge to map "
"features by coordinating mapping in the field."
msgstr ""
"Field Tasking Manager (Field-TM) husaidia timu kuongeza maarifa ya kienyeji "
"kwenye vipengele vya ramani kwa kuratibu uchoraji ramani uwanjani."

#: app/templates/landing.html:522
msgid ""
"Field-TM facilitates collaborative mapping by supporting and extending "
"mature tools like ODK and QField. It is a standalone mobile and web workflow"
" that helps teams collect geospatial data efficiently with commonly "
"available Android devices."
msgstr ""
"Field-TM huwezesha uchoraji ramani wa ushirikiano kwa kuunga mkono na "
"kupanua zana zilizokomaa kama ODK na QField. Ni mtiririko wa kazi wa simu na"
" wavuti wa kujitegemea unaosaidia timu kukusanya data ya kijiografia kwa "
"ufanisi kwa kutumia vifaa vya Android vinavyopatikana kwa kawaida."

#: app/templates/landing.html:527
msgid "A project manager demonstrates FieldTM mapping workflow on a laptop"
msgstr ""
"Msimamizi wa mradi anaonyesha mtiririko wa kazi wa uchoraji ramani wa "
"FieldTM kwenye kompyuta mpakato"

#: app/templates/landing.html:533
msgid "Main Features"
msgstr "Vipengele vikuu"

#: app/templates/landing.html:536
msgid "Flexible Data Collection"
msgstr "Ukusanyaji data wenye kubadilika"

#: app/templates/landing.html:538
msgid ""
"Support diverse survey forms, multiple data formats, and adaptable workflows"
" that fit different operational needs."
msgstr ""
"Inasaidia aina mbalimbali za fomu za utafiti, miundo mingi ya data, na "
"mtiririko wa kazi unaobadilika kulingana na mahitaji tofauti ya uendeshaji."

#: app/templates/landing.html:542
msgid "Open Source and Customizable"
msgstr "Chanzo huria na kinachoweza kubinafsishwa"

#: app/templates/landing.html:544
msgid ""
"Adapt Field-TM to your own survey logic, data structures, and integration "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"Badilisha Field-TM ilingane na mantiki yako ya utafiti, miundo ya data, na "
"mahitaji ya uunganishaji."

#: app/templates/landing.html:548
msgid "Entity-Level Tracking"
msgstr "Ufuatiliaji wa kiwango cha kipengele"

#: app/templates/landing.html:550
msgid ""
"Monitor survey progress at task and feature level so managers can make "
"informed decisions quickly."
msgstr ""
"Fuatilia maendeleo ya utafiti katika kiwango cha kazi na kipengele ili "
"mameneja waweze kufanya maamuzi sahihi haraka."

#: app/templates/landing.html:557
msgid "Who is it for?"
msgstr "Ni kwa ajili ya nani?"

#: app/templates/landing.html:560
msgid "Project Manager"
msgstr "Meneja wa mradi"

#: app/templates/landing.html:561
msgid "Create and coordinate field campaigns"
msgstr "Unda na uratibu kampeni za uwanjani"

#: app/templates/landing.html:563
msgid ""
"Project managers use Field-TM to set up mapping projects, define areas of "
"interest, design survey forms, and split work into manageable tasks."
msgstr ""
"Mameneja wa miradi hutumia Field-TM kuweka miradi ya uchoraji ramani, "
"kufafanua maeneo ya maslahi, kubuni fomu za utafiti, na kugawa kazi katika "
"majukumu yanayoweza kusimamiwa."

#: app/templates/landing.html:566
msgid "Define a project area and upload or choose a survey form"
msgstr "Fafanua eneo la mradi na upakie au uchague fomu ya utafiti"

#: app/templates/landing.html:567
msgid "Split the area into tasks and generate a data extract"
msgstr "Gawanya eneo katika kazi na uzalishe dondoo la data"

#: app/templates/landing.html:568
msgid "Publish the project to ODK Central or QFieldCloud"
msgstr "Chapisha mradi kwenye ODK Central au QFieldCloud"

#: app/templates/landing.html:569
msgid "Share a QR code so mappers can start collecting data"
msgstr "Shiriki msimbo wa QR ili wachoraji ramani waanze kukusanya data"

#: app/templates/landing.html:573
msgid "Field Mapper"
msgstr "Mchoraji ramani wa uwanjani"

#: app/templates/landing.html:574
msgid "Collect data in the field with your phone"
msgstr "Kusanya data uwanjani kwa kutumia simu yako"

#: app/templates/landing.html:576
msgid ""
"Mappers do not need to log in to Field-TM. Once a project manager publishes "
"a project, mappers access it directly in their mobile app of choice."
msgstr ""
"Wachoraji ramani hawahitaji kuingia kwenye Field-TM. Mara meneja wa mradi "
"anapochapisha mradi, wachoraji ramani huufikia moja kwa moja kwenye programu"
" yao ya simu wanayoichagua."

#: app/templates/landing.html:579
msgid "Scan the QR code shared by your project manager"
msgstr "Changanua msimbo wa QR ulioshirikiwa na meneja wako wa mradi"

#: app/templates/landing.html:580
msgid "The project loads automatically in ODK Collect or QField"
msgstr "Mradi unapakia kiotomatiki kwenye ODK Collect au QField"

#: app/templates/landing.html:581
msgid "Navigate to your assigned task area and collect data"
msgstr "Nenda kwenye eneo lako la kazi ulilopewa na ukusanye data"

#: app/templates/landing.html:582
msgid "Submit your survey, which goes straight to the server"
msgstr "Wasilisha utafiti wako, ambao huenda moja kwa moja kwenye seva"

#: app/templates/landing.html:589
msgid "Field-TM Use Cases"
msgstr "Matumizi ya Field-TM"

#: app/templates/landing.html:594
msgid "Field mapping in progress"
msgstr "Uchoraji ramani wa uwanjani unaendelea"

#: app/templates/landing.html:599
msgid "1. Community Mapping"
msgstr "1. Uchoraji ramani wa jamii"

#: app/templates/landing.html:601
msgid ""
"Field Tasking Manager empowers communities to map informal settlements, "
"public facilities, and local services for inclusive planning."
msgstr ""
"Field Tasking Manager huwezesha jamii kuchora ramani ya makazi yasiyo rasmi,"
" huduma za umma, na huduma za eneo kwa ajili ya mipango shirikishi."

#: app/templates/landing.html:605
msgid "2. Urban Planning and Management"
msgstr "2. Mipango na usimamizi wa miji"

#: app/templates/landing.html:607
msgid ""
"Build smarter cities with coordinated surveys of houses, roads, and "
"utilities through clear, manageable mapping tasks."
msgstr ""
"Jenga miji yenye akili zaidi kwa tafiti zilizoratibiwa za nyumba, barabara, "
"na huduma kupitia kazi za uchoraji ramani zilizo wazi na zinazoweza "
"kusimamiwa."

#: app/templates/landing.html:611
msgid "3. Disaster Response and Recovery"
msgstr "3. Mwitikio na urejeshaji baada ya maafa"

#: app/templates/landing.html:613
msgid ""
"Rapidly map damaged infrastructure after disasters, coordinate volunteers, "
"and deliver reliable data for relief operations."
msgstr ""
"Chora ramani kwa haraka ya miundombinu iliyoharibika baada ya maafa, ratibu "
"wajitolea, na toa data ya kuaminika kwa shughuli za msaada."

